---
---

<section id="positioning" class="positioning">
  <div class="positioning__wash"></div>
  <div class="container positioning__inner">
    <div class="positioning__grid">
      <figure class="positioning__media reveal">
        <img src="/images/waystation-exterior-2.png" alt="A Rangeway Waystation with a warm lounge facade and charging canopy set into the landscape" loading="lazy" />
      </figure>
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our thesis</p>
        <blockquote class="positioning__quote">
          We think like <em>hotel operators</em>, not utility companies. The stop should be worth
          the time.
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <aside class="positioning__aside reveal">
        <p>
          Every Rangeway location is designed the way a hospitality operator designs a property.
          Lighting, materials, service, sequence. The charging happens inside a space built for
          the people waiting, not outside in a lot built for the car.
        </p>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .positioning {
    background: var(--surface-alt);
    padding: clamp(92px, 12vw, 174px) 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .positioning__wash {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 85% 20%, rgba(244, 168, 85, 0.1), transparent 45%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .positioning__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(260px, 0.72fr) minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(260px, 0.62fr);
    gap: clamp(28px, 5vw, 72px);
    align-items: end;
  }

  .positioning__media {
    margin: 0;
    align-self: stretch;
    min-height: 420px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .positioning__media img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
  }

  .positioning__quote {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.8vw, 3.1rem);
    line-height: 1.18;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 20ch;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .positioning__quote em {
    color: var(--color-warm-deep);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .positioning__aside {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 440px;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .positioning__aside p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .positioning__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-6);
    }

    .positioning__media {
      min-height: 280px;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    }
  }
</style>
